Package: python-marytts
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Suggests: python-python-marytts-doc
Description: python-marytts is a HTTP based interface to MaryTTS (Python 2)
 A pretty simple HTTP based interface to MaryTTS intended to make using this
 excellent TTS for waveform and IPA generation as convenient as possible.
 Target audience are developers who would like to use MaryTTS as-is for speech
 synthesis in their Python application on GNU/Linux operating systems.
 .
 This package installs the library for Python 2.

